::Hakibuscon::
(OOC: Dinobot, how come you didn't respond or react to the two missiles I
shot at you while you were swinging through the trees?  Or we can just say
that you didn't notice them?)

	"Damnit!  I wasn't even close to hitting them!" Hakibuscon screamed in
anger.

	Hakibuscon went chasing after them in vehicle mode until he saw a
beautiful place that looked trashed by some other faction.  And he saw
Dinobot and Tavatron.  Hakibuscon went into robot mode and jumped out in
front of them.

	"Well, well, well.  What have we got here?  Have you two been loving on
the job?  I bet your leader won't like that!  But don't worry, I am not
going to tell your leader.  It won't matter if you two are piles of
SCRAAAAPPPP!!!!!" Hakibuscon yelled and fired another missile at
them.(Hakibuscon is 15 feet away from them so they better react fast, or at
least react at all this time!)
